Psalm 37:27 . . . "Turn away from what is bad and do what is good, And so reside to time indefinite." They would not be involved in anything that is displeasing in God's eyes. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/44/Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-3.jpg/v4-459px-Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-3.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/4/44/Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-3.jpg/v4-759px-Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

(Psalm 119:97) . . . "How I do love your law! All day long it is my concern." They read the Bible with understanding and they stick closely to all of the principles of the Bible. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/80/Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-4.jpg/v4-459px-Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-4.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/8/80/Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-4.jpg/v4-759px-Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-4.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

(1 Corinthians 15:33) . . . "Do not be misled. Bad associations spoil useful habits." They would encourage you to do what God says all the time and will be willing to correct a friend at times if needed. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a3/Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-5.jpg/v4-459px-Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-5.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/a/a3/Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-5.jpg/v4-759px-Choose-a-Spouse-According-to-the-Bible-Step-5.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
